Q1: At first I was asked to pick between two shapes, one having more points then the other. Then I had to choose between two letters on my keyboard D and F, D being for numbers less than 153, and F being for more than 153. After this, it was letters closer to A or closer to Z. If it was A then you picked J, if it Z then you picked K. Then you had to do both of these things, but making sure you went fast to gain the point from the original shapes.
